## Implementation Guide

### Data Sources

#### KPI Cards Section
- **API Endpoint**: `GET /api/fleet/firmware-updates/summary/`
- **Fields Used**:
  - `available_firmware_count` - Total number of available firmware packages
  - `outdated_devices_count` - Devices with updates available
  - `updating_now_count` - Devices currently updating

#### Filters
- **Search Filter**:
  - **Implementation**: Searches version, component, description, etc.
  
- **Component Filter**:
  - **Query Parameter**: `component=obd|dashcam|other`
  - **Values**: All, OBD, Dashcam, Vehicle ECU, Other
  - **Documentation Reference**: `component` field in firmware.md
  
- **Status Filter**:
  - **Query Parameter**: `status=paused|rolling_out|completed`
  - **Values**: All, Paused, Rolling Out, Completed
  - **Documentation Reference**: `status` field in firmware.md
  
- **Version Filter**:
  - **Query Parameter**: `version=<value>`
  - **Implementation**: Search by version string

- **Release Date Filter**:
  - **Query Parameter**: `release_date_after=<date>&release_date_before=<date>`
  - **Values**: Any, Last 30 days, Last 90 days, Custom Range
  - **Documentation Reference**: `release_date` field in firmware.md

#### Firmware Packages Table
- **API Endpoint**: `GET /api/fleet/firmware-updates/`
- **Query Parameters**: All filters applied
- **Columns**:
  - Checkbox for selection
  - Version
  - Device Type (component)
  - Release Date
  - Size (file_size)
  - Status
  - View Action
  
- **Row Actions**:
  - View: Navigate to firmware package detail page

#### Bulk Actions Dropdown
- **Delete Selected**:
  - **API**: Multiple calls to `DELETE /api/fleet/firmware-updates/{id}/`
  - **Documentation Reference**: Base endpoints section in firmware.md
  
- **Pause Selected**:
  - **API**: Multiple calls to `POST /api/fleet/firmware-updates/{id}/pause/`
  - **Documentation Reference**: Pause/Resume section in firmware.md
  
- **Resume Selected**:
  - **API**: Multiple calls to `POST /api/fleet/firmware-updates/{id}/resume/`
  - **Documentation Reference**: Pause/Resume section in firmware.md

#### Device Update Status
- **API Endpoint**: `GET /api/fleet/firmware-updates/installs/`
- **Purpose**: Shows a summary of devices being updated
- **Documentation Reference**: `installs[]` field in firmware.md detail section

#### Update History
- **API Endpoint**: `GET /api/fleet/firmware-updates/history/`
- **Purpose**: Shows a summary of recent update activities

### API Alignment
All endpoints and fields used in this design match the documentation in firmware.md:
- `GET /api/fleet/firmware-updates/` - List firmware updates
- `GET /api/fleet/firmware-updates/summary/` - Get summary stats
- `POST /api/fleet/firmware-updates/{id}/pause/` - Pause update
- `POST /api/fleet/firmware-updates/{id}/resume/` - Resume update
- `DELETE /api/fleet/firmware-updates/{id}/` - Delete update
